---
import '../assets/css/pages/brand.css';
import ColorSwatch from '../components/ColorSwatch.astro';
import HtmlHead from '../components/HtmlHead.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
import OldStyleButtons from '../components/OldStyleButtons.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
import SvgDefs from '../components/SvgDefs.astro';
import TextSwatch from '../components/TextSwatch.astro';
import Webrings from '../components/Webrings.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPage">
	<HtmlHead
		title="Brand | Marco Campos"
		description="Logo and Brand for Marco Campos website."
		tags={['brand', 'logo']}
	/>
	<body>
		<a href="/yapping" rel="nofollow" hidden>Don't follow this link</a>

		<skip-to-content>
			<a href="#main">Skip to main content</a>
		</skip-to-content>

		<SiteNav />

		<css-naked-day>
			<hr />
			<h2>Why this website looks so weird?</h2>
			<p>We are celebrating CSS Naked Day!</p>
			<p>Find out more on <a href="/blog/2025/04/css-naked-day-2025/">this blog post</a>.</p>
			<hr />
		</css-naked-day>

		<header>
			<Logo
				subtitle="Branding"
				shortSubtitle="Brand"
				title="Branding"
			/>
			<h1>Brand & Logo</h1>
		</header>

		<main id="main">
			<h2 id="general">General Info</h2>

			<p>The idea is to just have fun while using some nice colours and styles.</p>
			<p>Keeping everything as accessible and consistent as possible is paramount.</p>
			<p>That's it, nothing much to be said...</p>
			<p>I mean, it is a personal brand for a developer, so it has to be techy and "modern" as well I suppose.</p>

			<h2 id="colours">Colours</h2>

			<color-swatch-group>
				<ColorSwatch color="#0080ff" name="Blissful Blue" />
				<ColorSwatch color="#ff8000" name="Zany Orange" />
				<ColorSwatch color="#00309b" name="Slumbering Blue" />
				<ColorSwatch color="#f03e3e" name="Whacky Red" />
			</color-swatch-group>

			<h2 id="fonts">Fonts</h2>

			<TextSwatch font="Mecano" fontFamily="'Mecano-Light', 'Mecano', monospace" />
			<TextSwatch font="Selawik" fontFamily="'Selawik Variable', 'Selawik', 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Open Sans', 'Arial', system-ui, sans-serif" />
			<TextSwatch font="Cascadia Code" fontFamily="'Cascadia Code', 'Fira Code', 'Roboto Mono', 'Monaco', 'Courier New', 'Courier', monospace" />

			<h2 id="icons">Icons</h2>

			<p>Icons are from the <a href="https://www.mingcute.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MingCute</a> icon library, with the <em>line</em> style.</p>

			<h2 id="logo">Logo</h2>

			<p>The logo is available on the following sizes and styles:</p>

			<dl>
				<dt>Full Size</dt>
				<dd>
					Contains the full moniker, "madcampos", composed of all the initials of my name and the full last name, with extra details depending on the style. The default
					extra is a pair of curly braces.
				</dd>

				<dt>Mini Size</dt>
				<dd>
					Is an abbreviation of the moniker to only the initials of the name, "madc", with extra details depending on the style. The default extra is a pair of curly
					braces.
				</dd>

				<dt>Micro Size</dt>
				<dd>Only an "m", with extras, depending on the style. The default is extra is a pair of curly braces.</dd>

				<dt>Glitch Style</dt>
				<dd>An style applied to the logo to add a glitch annimation to it. This is the style used on the error pages.</dd>

				<dt>Themes</dt>
				<dd>All themes include a customized logo in all sizes.</dd>
			</dl>

			<h3>Logo Gallery</h3>

			<m-note data-type="info">
				<p>
					<strong>Note:</strong> The logos may be affected by accessibility settings.
				</p>
			</m-note>

			<details open>
				<summary>Default Logo</summary>

				<article class="logo-container" data-theme="system">
					<Logo
						title="Branding"
						subtitle="Branding"
						shortSubtitle="Brand"
						url={Astro.url.pathname}
						setSvgSize
						full
						theme="system"
					/>
					<Logo
						title="Branding"
						subtitle="Branding"
						shortSubtitle="Brand"
						url={Astro.url.pathname}
						setSvgSize
						mini
						theme="system"
					/>
					<Logo
						title="Branding"
						subtitle="Branding"
						shortSubtitle="Brand"
						url={Astro.url.pathname}
						setSvgSize
						micro
						theme="system"
					/>
					<Logo
						title="Branding"
						subtitle="Branding"
						shortSubtitle="Brand"
						url={Astro.url.pathname}
						setSvgSize
						micro
						glitch
						theme="system"
					/>
				</article>
			</details>

			<details>
				<summary>High Contrast Logo</summary>

				<article class="logo-container" data-theme="high-contrast">
